overview: Clad in their signature cowboy hats, Mexican boy band Conjunto Atardecer presents videos of their newest hits alongside the classics that launched their career, spread over a multidisc set. Tracks include "Hoja en Blanco," "Las Flores Que Te Llevaba," "Adiós Amor," "El Profeta," "Dario Ibarra," "Ignacio Remédios," "El Centenario," "Ramiro Sierra," "Jesus Rubio" and "Bola de Gatos Rayados." Extras include three promotional music videos.
title: Conjunto Atardecer: Cantan Corridos II
